### Spec: `content.integration` (Phoenix exercises v4)\
\
**Purpose:** close the practice with grounded carry-forward behavior *without promises*.\
\
**Required structure (exercise render order unchanged):**\
`intro \uc0\u8594  guided_practice \u8594  aha_noticing \u8594  integration`\
\
**Constraints**\
\
* **Second person**, **present tense**\
* **No outcome claims**, no \'93you will\'94, no \'93this will fix\'94, no \'93healed\'94\
* **No identity transformation**\
* **No emotional climax / motivational lift**\
* **No new teaching** (integration is carry-forward + boundary, not a new lesson)\
\
**Word counts**\
\
* `min_words: 40`\
* `preferred_word_range: [60, 120]`\
* `max_words: 150`\
\
**Required opener (callout)**\
Integration must start with one of these (same \'93structural moment\'94 feel as AHA):\
\
* \'93Now, before you move on,\'94\
* \'93Now, as you return,\'94\
* \'93Now, for the next few minutes,\'94\
* \'93Now, as you go back to your day,\'94\
* \'93Now, keep it simple,\'94\
\
**Required content pattern**\
\
* **Carry-forward cue:** one micro-action that fits the exercise (e.g., \'93one longer exhale\'94, \'93soften jaw once\'94, \'93feel feet at red lights\'94)\
* **Boundary clause:** \'93Nothing has to change.\'94 / \'93No need to force it.\'94 / \'93If it\'92s not there today, that\'92s fine.\'94\
* **Re-entry:** how to rejoin the environment (screen, hallway, meeting) without \'93reset fantasy\'94\
